---
title: HelloHero: Italian Beef, Bacon & Potato-Top Pie with Baby Leaves & Parmesan Topping
description: Sometimes only a pie will do. Satisfy that craving for something warm, herby and comforting with this rich, cheesy mash-topped number. It's Nonna's cooking fused with an explosion of flavour and a dinner that reminds us why at-home cooking is best.

